text: François de Mazières (born 22 May 1960) is a French politician. He serves as a member of the National Assembly, representing Yvelines since June 2012. He is mayor of Versailles since March 2008. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:People from Tarbes Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:Sciences Po alumni Category:Panthéon-Assas University alumni Category:École nationale d'administration alumni Category:Mayors of places in Île-de-France Category:Union for French Democracy politicians Category:Chevaliers of the Légion d'honneur Category:Officiers of the Ordre des Arts et des Lettres Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
